snippet.title: Hay Day Pop: So Satisfying
snippet.description:

Be a POP STAR! Subscribe! ►► https://supr.cl/HayDayPopYoutube

Welcome to Hay Day Pop! Where the hour is always golden, and the only problems are puzzle problems.
Let’s pop! Match and solve challenging puzzles with endless surprises! Harvest crops and complete deliveries to reap big rewards. Endless possibilities to design and customize the farm of your dreams. Purchase cute cows, buzzing bumblebees, and plump piggies to populate your own slice of paradise! 
Use your wits and boosters to keep your puzzle win streak alive. Earn star rewards and pop your way up the leaderboards and all the way to each season’s Diamond Star Race!
